#include<iostream>
#define max(a,b) a>b?a:b
#define min(a,b) a<b?a:b
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int t;
    int x1,y1,x2,y2,x3,y3,x4,y4,x5,x6,y5,y6;
    cin>>t;
    while(t--)
    {
              cin>>x1>>y1>>x2>>y2;
              cin>>x3>>y3>>x4>>y4;
              x5=max(x1,x3);
              y5=max(y1,y3);
              x6=min(x2,x4);
              y6=min(y2,y4);
              if((x5<x6)&&(y5<y6))cout <<x5<<" "<<y5<<" "<<x6<<" "<<y6;
              else cout<<"No Overlap";
              cout<<"\n";
    }
}
